    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Early alarm and the rumble of surf. I heard the surf arrive in the night and have been excited for the alarm to ring. Coffee and a walk down with Zanzi to the point to watch the waves. It’s pretty big and wild, the wind not yet blowing. There are some rogue sets that clean up the bay but they don’t seem as frequent as the other day.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Early alarm and the rumble of surf. I heard the surf arrive in the night and have been excited for the alarm to ring. Coffee and a walk down with Zanzi to the point to watch the waves. It’s pretty big and wild, the wind not yet blowing. There are some rogue sets that clean up the bay but they don’t seem as frequent as the other day.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
