          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Filen and I start speaking casually at first, but I had some questions that I wanted to ask him and and our talking shifts to speaking about our understanding of the truths to life. He makes an interesting point about free will maybe existing if we have the true ability to direct our attention?",
